(51, 'PHP Arrays', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20170101/PHP Arrays.pdf', '1.4 MB', '168', '2016', 'English', 'PDF', 53, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/PHP-Arrays.jpg', 'Gain an in-depth understanding of PHP 7 arrays. After a quick overview of PHP 7, each chapter concentrates on single, multi-dimensional, associative, and object arrays. PHP Arrays is a first of its kind book using PHP 7 that demonstrates inserting, appending, updating, and deleting array data.', 0, 0),
(52, 'PHP Beyond the Web', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20161222/PHP Beyond the Web.pdf', '11.3 MB', '214', '2016', 'English', 'PDF', 53, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/PHP-Beyond-the-Web.jpg', '\nUse your existing web-based PHP skills to write all types of software: CLI scripts, desktop software, network servers, and more. This book gives you the tools, techniques, and background necessary to write just about any type of software you can think of, using the PHP you know.', 0, 0),
(53, 'PHP Persistence', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20161220/PHP Persistence.pdf', '1.1 MB', '107', '2017', 'English', 'PDF', 53, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/PHP-Persistence.jpg', 'Take the pain out of dealing with relational databases in an object-oriented programming world. With this short book, you can save time and money by simply coding less while accomplishing more with the Doctrine persistence framework, a leadingpersistence solution for PHP programmers and web developers. PHP Persistence teaches you about PHP persistence and how to use it effectively for your database-driven applications.', 0, 0),
