(127, 'Bootstrap Essentials', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150814/Bootstrap Essentials.pdf', '5.39 MB', '166', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 5, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1439/5655cde36ab0d94.jpeg', 'This book will familiarize you with all the features, functionalities, and architectural knowledge of the Bootstrap platform. You will begin by discovering the mobile-first philosophy and what Bootstrap is. You will learn about Bootstrap&#8217;s architecture and components, and how to use Bootstrap with LESS. You will create responsive layouts using Bootstrap CSS and work with the packaged components that come along with Bootstrap. You will proceed to explore the various JavaScript components and add-ons offered by Bootstrap. Finally, you will learn how to customize Bootstrap, compile and build your Bootstrap code, and extend Bootstrap with different extensions to create more advanced websites.', 0, 0),
(128, 'Learning Web Development with Bootstrap and AngularJS', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150811/Learning Web Development with Bootstrap and AngularJS.pdf', '10.6 MB', '224', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 5, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1439/7555c99abf00385.jpeg', 'If you&#8217;re ready to progress your web development skills past HTML and CSS, this book will give you everything you need to build your own web app. You&#8217;ll be taught the basics of Bootstrap and AngularJS, taking an in-depth look at what makes up each framework. After you&#8217;ve mastered the ideology, you&#8217;ll put it into action as you build a contact manager throughout the course of the book.', 0, 0),
(129, 'Learning Web Development with Bootstrap and AngularJS', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150811/Learning Web Development with Bootstrap and AngularJS.pdf', '10.6 MB', '224', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 1, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1439/7555c99abf00385.jpeg', 'If you&#8217;re ready to progress your web development skills past HTML and CSS, this book will give you everything you need to build your own web app. You&#8217;ll be taught the basics of Bootstrap and AngularJS, taking an in-depth look at what makes up each framework. After you&#8217;ve mastered the ideology, you&#8217;ll put it into action as you build a contact manager throughout the course of the book.', 0, 0),
(130, 'ASP.NET MVC 5 with Bootstrap and Knockout.js', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150811/ASPdotNET MVC 5 with Bootstrap and Knockoutdotjs.pdf', '3.67 MB', '278', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 5, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1439/7555c9996b778fc.jpeg', 'Bring dynamic server-side web content and responsive web design together to build websites that work and display well on any resolution, desktop or mobile. With this practical book, you’ll learn how by combining the ASP.NET MVC server-side language, the Bootstrap front-end framework, and Knockout.js—the JavaScript implementation of the Model-View-ViewModel pattern.', 0, 0),
(131, 'ASP.NET MVC 5 with Bootstrap and Knockout.js', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150811/ASPdotNET MVC 5 with Bootstrap and Knockoutdotjs.pdf', '3.67 MB', '278', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 2, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1439/7555c9996b778fc.jpeg', 'Bring dynamic server-side web content and responsive web design together to build websites that work and display well on any resolution, desktop or mobile. With this practical book, you’ll learn how by combining the ASP.NET MVC server-side language, the Bootstrap front-end framework, and Knockout.js—the JavaScript implementation of the Model-View-ViewModel pattern.', 0, 0),
(132, 'ASP.NET MVC 5 with Bootstrap and Knockout.js', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150811/ASPdotNET MVC 5 with Bootstrap and Knockoutdotjs.pdf', '3.67 MB', '278', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 23, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1439/7555c9996b778fc.jpeg', 'Bring dynamic server-side web content and responsive web design together to build websites that work and display well on any resolution, desktop or mobile. With this practical book, you’ll learn how by combining the ASP.NET MVC server-side language, the Bootstrap front-end framework, and Knockout.js—the JavaScript implementation of the Model-View-ViewModel pattern.', 0, 0),
(133, 'Bootstrap Site Blueprints', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150626/Bootstrap Site Blueprints.pdf', '8.6 MB', '304', '2014', 'English', 'PDF', 5, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1435/26558d582db010f.jpg', 'Since its debut in August 2011, Twitter Bootstrap, now simply Bootstrap, has become by far the most popular framework for empowering and enhancing frontend web design. With Version 3, Bootstrap reaches an exciting new milestone, introducing a mobile-first responsive grid, new and powerful LESS mixins, and a lean code base optimized for modern browsers.', 0, 0),
(134, 'CakePHP 2 Application Cookbook', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150907/CakePHP 2 Application Cookbook.pdf', '3.86 MB', '346', '2014', 'English', 'PDF', 7, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/CakePHP-2-Application-Cookbook.jpg', 'CakePHP is the most popular rapid application development framework for PHP. For over 10 years, this open source project has been the go-to solution for quickly and easily building websites and web applications.', 0, 0),
(135, 'CakePHP 2 Application Cookbook', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150907/CakePHP 2 Application Cookbook.pdf', '3.86 MB', '346', '2014', 'English', 'PDF', 53, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/CakePHP-2-Application-Cookbook.jpg', 'CakePHP is the most popular rapid application development framework for PHP. For over 10 years, this open source project has been the go-to solution for quickly and easily building websites and web applications.', 0, 0),
(136, 'CakePHP Application Development', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150506/CakePHP Application Development.pdf', '6.88 MB', '332', '2008', 'English', 'PDF', 7, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CakePHP-Application-Development.jpg', 'This book offers step-by-step instructions to learn the CakePHP framework and to quickly develop and deploy web-based applications. It introduces the MVC pattern and coding styles using practical examples. It takes the developer through setting up a CakePHP development and deployment environment, and develops an example application to illustrate all of the techniques you need to write a complete, non-trivial application in PHP. It aims to assist PHP programmers to rapidly develop and deploy well-crafted and robust web-based applications with CakePHP.', 0, 0),
(137, 'CakePHP Application Development', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150506/CakePHP Application Development.pdf', '6.88 MB', '332', '2008', 'English', 'PDF', 53, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CakePHP-Application-Development.jpg', 'This book offers step-by-step instructions to learn the CakePHP framework and to quickly develop and deploy web-based applications. It introduces the MVC pattern and coding styles using practical examples. It takes the developer through setting up a CakePHP development and deployment environment, and develops an example application to illustrate all of the techniques you need to write a complete, non-trivial application in PHP. It aims to assist PHP programmers to rapidly develop and deploy well-crafted and robust web-based applications with CakePHP.', 0, 0),
(138, 'Practical CakePHP Projects', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150506/Practical CakePHP Projects.pdf', '6 MB', '400', '2008', 'English', 'PDF', 7, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Practical-CakePHP-Projects.jpg', 'If you&#8217;ve been using PHP for sometime now and would like to start using a web framework, you&#8217;ll want to try CakePHP, which is an open source rapid development web framework built on PHP.', 0, 0),
(139, 'Practical CakePHP Projects', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150506/Practical CakePHP Projects.pdf', '6 MB', '400', '2008', 'English', 'PDF', 53, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Practical-CakePHP-Projects.jpg', 'If you&#8217;ve been using PHP for sometime now and would like to start using a web framework, you&#8217;ll want to try CakePHP, which is an open source rapid development web framework built on PHP.', 0, 0),
(140, 'CherryPy Essentials', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150514/CherryPy Essentials.pdf', '5.2 MB', '272', '2007', 'English', 'PDF', 8, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1431/68555585a47b26a.jpg', 'CherryPy is a Python library for web development that allows developers to build web applications in the same way as any other object-oriented Python program. Enriched by several years of active development, it has become one of the most established toolkits for building solid and high-performance web applications in Python. CherryPy abstracts the complex low-level HTTP protocol into an easy-to-use interface that respects Python idioms. The library aims at being simple to learn for a beginner while offering the most advanced features to fluent Python developers. For these reasons CherryPy was chosen to be at the heart of the popular and feature-rich TurboGears web framework. CherryPy-powered web applications are stand-alone Python applications with their own embedded multi-threaded web server, but can also run behind Apache or IIS for scalability.', 0, 0),
(141, 'Programming with CodeIgniter MVC', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160228/Programming with CodeIgniter MVC.pdf', '4.58 MB', '193', '2013', 'English', 'PDF', 9, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/Programming-with-CodeIgniter-MVC.jpg', 'The CodeIgniter Model-View-Controller framework provides genius simplicity, flexibility, and efficient resource usage, boosting performance and reusability.', 0, 0),
(142, 'CodeIgniter Web Application Blueprints', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150907/CodeIgniter Web Application Blueprints.pdf', '1.95 MB', '330', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 9, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/CodeIgniter-Web-Application-Blueprints.jpg', 'Loosely based on the Model-View-Controller pattern, CodeIgniter is an open source framework for application development. It allows you to develop projects by providing a rich set of libraries for common tasks, including a simple interface and logical structure to access these libraries.', 0, 0),
(143, 'CodeIgniter for Rapid PHP Application Development', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150507/CodeIgniter for Rapid PHP Application Development.pdf', '3.6 MB', '260', '2007', 'English', 'PDF', 9, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CodeIgniter-for-Rapid-PHP-Application-Development.jpg', 'CodeIgniter (CI) is a powerful open-source PHP framework with a very small footprint, built for PHP coders who need a simple and elegant toolkit to create full-featured web applications. CodeIgniter is an MVC framework, similar in some ways to the Rails framework for Ruby, and is designed to enable, not overwhelm.', 0, 0),
(144, 'CodeIgniter for Rapid PHP Application Development', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150507/CodeIgniter for Rapid PHP Application Development.pdf', '3.6 MB', '260', '2007', 'English', 'PDF', 53, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/CodeIgniter-for-Rapid-PHP-Application-Development.jpg', 'CodeIgniter (CI) is a powerful open-source PHP framework with a very small footprint, built for PHP coders who need a simple and elegant toolkit to create full-featured web applications. CodeIgniter is an MVC framework, similar in some ways to the Rails framework for Ruby, and is designed to enable, not overwhelm.', 0, 0),
(145, 'CoffeeScript in Action', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160607/CoffeeScript in Action.pdf', '10.45 MB', '432', '2014', 'English', 'PDF', 10, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1465/3557573fa841967.jpeg', 'CoffeeScript in Action is a tutorial that teaches you how, where, and why to use CoffeeScript. It begins by quickly exposing you to CoffeeScript&#8217;s new, but instantly-familiar syntax. Then, you&#8217;ll explore programming challenges that illustrate CoffeeScript&#8217;s unique advantages. Language junkies will especially appreciate how this book takes idioms from other programming languages and shows you how CoffeeScript makes them available in JavaScript.', 0, 0),
(146, 'CoffeeScript Application Development Cookbook', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20151020/CoffeeScript Application Development Cookbook.pdf', '4.08 MB', '368', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 10, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1445/245625e735126f0.jpeg', 'CoffeeScript is a JavaScript compiler. CoffeeScript brings many things to the table that are lacking in JavaScript itself. This includes a class and module system, a syntax that is cleaner, less terse, and well structured, and list comprehensions that make working with collections of data more enjoyable. CoffeeScript can be used as not only a tool for the Web, but also as a tool for day-to-day DevOps type tasks (for example, file processing, working with databases, and more).', 0, 0),
(147, 'Django Project Blueprints', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20170307/Django Project Blueprints.pdf', '4.4 MB', '264', '2016', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Django-Project-Blueprints-400x493.jpg', 'Django is a high-level web framework that eases the creation of complex, database-driven websites. It emphasizes on the reusability and pluggability of components, rapid development, and the principle of don&#8217;t repeat yourself. It lets you build high-performing, elegant web applications quickly.', 0, 0),
(148, 'Learning Website Development with Django', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160416/Learning Website Development with Django.pdf', '2.99 MB', '264', '2008', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1460/6557118189e7854.jpg', 'This book is a beginner&#8217;s guide to design, develop, and deploy a fully-featured dynamic website using the features of Django. This book is for web developers who want to see how to build a complete site with Web 2.0 features, using the power of a proven and popular development system, but do not necessarily want to learn how a complete framework functions in order to do this. Basic knowledge of Python development is required for this book, but no knowledge of Django is expected.', 0, 0),
(149, 'Beginning Django CMS', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160130/Beginning Django CMS.pdf', '5.93 MB', '175', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1454/8756ad22a39489d.jpeg', 'Build a world-class website in less than a week with Django CMS.', 0, 0),
(150, 'Django By Example', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160104/Django By Example.rar', '6.77 MB', '474', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1451/41568adfb42f9ea.jpeg', 'Django is a powerful Python web framework designed to develop web applications quickly, from simple prototypes to large-scale projects. Django encourages clean, pragmatic design, and provides developers with a comprehensive set of tools to build scalable web applications.', 0, 0),
(151, 'Test-Driven Development with Django', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150913/Test Driven Development with Django.pdf', '4.15 MB', '186', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1442/7155f5cb5ae692c.jpeg', 'Test-Driven Development (TDD) simplifies the trickiest of software tasks with its unique ability to peel back problems into layers. The testing tools available in Python and Django make test writing a joy, and the full coverage test suite that results from TDD is a boon to any project.', 0, 0),
(152, 'Learning Django Web Development', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150731/Learning Django Web Development.pdf', '5.71 MB', '405', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1438/0755bc5c0915ee0.jpeg', 'Django, written in Python, is a web application framework designed to build complex web applications quickly without any hassle. It loosely follows the MVC pattern and adheres to the Don&#8217;t Repeat Yourself principle, which makes a database-driven application efficient and highly scalable, and is by far the most popular and mature Python web framework.', 0, 0),
(153, 'Lightweight Django', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150514/Lightweight Django.pdf', '4.4 MB', '246', '2014', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1431/685555872581347.jpg', 'How can you take advantage of the Django framework to integrate complex client-side interactions and real-time features into your web applications? Through a series of rapid application development projects, this hands-on book shows experienced Django developers how to include REST APIs, WebSockets, and client-side MVC frameworks such as Backbone.js into new or existing projects.', 0, 0),
(154, 'Pro Django, 2nd Edition', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150514/Pro Django, 2nd Edition.pdf', '3.3 MB', '300', '2013', 'English', 'PDF', 11, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1431/685555869b1a072.jpg', 'Learn how to leverage Django, the leading Python web application development framework, to its full potential in this advanced tutorial and reference. Updated for Django 1.5 and Python 3, Pro Django, Second Edition examines in great detail the complex problems that Python web application developers can face and how to solve them. It provides in-depth information about advanced tools and techniques available in every Django installation, running the gamut from the theory of Django&#8217;s internal operations to actual code that solves real-world problems for high-volume environments.', 0, 0),
(155, 'Enterprise Drupal 8 Development', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20170523/Enterprise Drupal 8 Development.pdf', '9.1 MB', '309', '2017', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/Enterprise-Drupal-8-Development.jpg', 'Successfully architect a Drupal 8 website that scales to meet project requirements of any size and scope.', 0, 0),
(156, 'Programmer&#8217;s Guide to Drupal, 2nd Edition', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20170320/Programmer\'s Guide to Drupal, 2nd Edition.pdf', '2.1 MB', '238', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Programmers-Guide-to-Drupal-2nd-Edition.jpg', 'If you’re a web programmer, your experiences have taught you certain lessons—and only some of them apply well to Drupal. Drupal has its own set of programming principles that require a different approach, and many programmers make mistakes when relying on skills they’ve used for other projects. This book will show you which programming techniques you can use—and which you should avoid—when building web applications with this popular content management framework.', 0, 0),
(157, 'Drupal 6 Search Engine Optimization', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20170130/Drupal 6 Search Engine Optimization.pdf', '8.9 MB', '280', '2009', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Drupal-6-Search-Engine-Optimization.jpg', 'This is a practical, hands-on book based around sound SEO techniques specifically applied to Drupal. Each chapter starts with a brief overview of the important concepts then quickly moves into practical step-by-step actions you can take immediately. Throughout the book, you&#8217;ll get clear instructions and detailed screenshots, so you can see exactly what to do each step of the way. You will install and configure a selection of Drupal modules ? each of which will move you one step closer to optimization. Chapter-by-chapter, your Drupal site will become more optimized so that by the end of the book, your site is 100% ready for Google. This book is written for Drupal site owners and those who create Drupal sites including themers, developers, programmers, and consultants. A basic understanding of Drupal will be helpful: what a node is, how to create nodes, how to log in to the admin sections of your Drupal site, and how to properly install and enable a module. No knowledge of SEO will be assumed but a basic knowledge of search engines is expected.', 0, 0),
(158, 'Drupal Intranets with Open Atrium', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20161215/Drupal Intranets with Open Atrium.pdf', '15.6 MB', '304', '2011', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Drupal-Intranets-with-Open-Atrium-400x494.jpg', 'In today&#8217;s global society, online collaboration has gained tremendous importance as businesses look for ways to share ideas and collaborate easily. Open Atrium is a powerful and flexible Drupal installation that provides intranet solutions to businesses and organizations for sharing ideas. It is used to create intranets where co-workers or teams can collaborate easily. But Open Atrium is filled with so many powerful features that you may need some help to use it to its full potential. Open Atrium is also a viable alternative to SharePoint.', 0, 0),
(159, 'Drupal 8 Development Cookbook', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160813/Drupal 8 Development Cookbook.pdf', '6.6 MB', '370', '2016', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/08/Drupal-8-Development-Cookbook-400x494.jpg', 'Began as a message board, Drupal today is open source software maintained and developed by a community of over 1,000,000 users and developers. Drupal is used by numerous local businesses to global corporations and diverse organizations all across the globe. With Drupal 8’s recent release and the exciting features it brings, this book will be your go-to guide to experimenting with all of these features through helpful recipes.', 0, 0),
(160, 'Drupal 7 Themes', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160811/Drupal 7 Themes.pdf', '7.9 MB', '316', '2011', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1470/9957ac251448a0d.jpg', 'Drupal is an award winning open source Content Management System (CMS). Based on PHP and MySQL, its power and flexibility combined with its exceptional design mean it is one of the most popular choices for creating a CMS website..', 0, 0),
(161, 'Drupal 7 Multilingual Sites', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160605/Drupal 7 Multilingual Sites.pdf', '2.16 MB', '140', '2012', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Drupal-7-Multilingual-Sites.jpg', 'A practical book with plenty of screenshots to guide you through the many features of multilingual Drupal. A demo ecommerce site is provided if you want to practice on a sample site, although you can apply the techniques learnt in the book directly to your site too. Any Drupal users who know the basics of building a Drupal site and are familiar with the Drupal UI, will benefit from this book. No previous knowledge of localization or internationalization is required.', 0, 0),
(162, 'Drupal 7 Mobile Web Development Beginner&#8217;s Guide', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160605/Drupal 7 Mobile Web Development Beginner-s Guide.pdf', '16.76 MB', '339', '2012', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/Drupal-7-Mobile-Web-Development-Beginners-Guide.jpg', 'Follow the fun example of a family pizza restaurant to help you adapt your own website to one that is fullyfunctional in a mobile environment. Each chapter covers a different aspect of mobile web development with plenty of step-by-step instructions and screenshots to make things clearer. This book is for independent developers who may or may not have had experience with Drupal websites. We take some deep dives into customized functionality that will take your Drupal development and your development workflow to the next level.', 0, 0),
(163, 'Drupal 7 Cookbook', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160605/Drupal 7 Cookbook.pdf', '5.35 MB', '324', '2012', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/1849517967.jpg', 'Drupal 7 is a modern Content Management System famed for its flexibility and power. Using Drupal you can easily create custom functionality that would otherwise have to be purchased in many of the other leading CMSs.', 0, 0),
(164, 'Pro Drupal as an Enterprise Development Platform', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20160514/Pro Drupal as an Enterprise Development Platform.pdf', '12.57 MB', '276', '2013', 'English', 'PDF', 12, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1463/175736ed53560c5.jpeg', 'In Pro Drupal as an Enterprise Development Platform authors Jamie Kurtz and Thomas Besluau explain how developers can save themselves time and money, and build their applications faster with fewer bugs by using the Drupal CMS as a foundation for their projects. The days when custom client applications were built entirely from scratch are over. Today, it makes business sense to use a flexible, highly scalable framework such as Drupal, Joomla or DotNetNuke as a foundation. This book focuses on why Drupal makes a particularly strong choice for the majority of developers.', 0, 0),
(165, 'Learning ExtJS, 4th Edition', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150829/Learning ExtJS, 4th Edition.pdf', '15.29 MB', '453', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 13, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1440/3255e15aa1869a4.jpg', 'The new Sencha Ext JS 5 library offers hundreds of components and APIs to build robust applications and fulfills the critical needs of customers all around the world. The new version 5 is packed with new themes and the MVVM architecture that allows you to connect the model layer to the view and automatically update the model when the view is modified and vice versa.', 0, 0),
(166, 'Mastering ExtJS, 2nd Edition', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150612/Mastering ExtJS, 2nd Edition.pdf', '12.8 MB', '529', '2015', 'English', 'PDF', 13, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1434/90557a7bfe6ba19.jpg', 'This book will help you to utilize Ext JS to its full potential and will show you how to create a complete Ext JS application from scratch.', 0, 0),
(167, 'Ext JS 4 Plugin and Extension Development', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20151017/Ext JS 4 Plugin and Extension Development.pdf', '3.83 MB', '116', '2013', 'English', 'PDF', 13, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1445/515621bc516c4c5.jpeg', 'Ext JS is a pure JavaScript application framework for building interactive web applications using techniques such as Ajax, DHTML, and DOM scripting.', 0, 0),
