(170, 'Enterprise Application Development with Ext JS and Spring', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150530/Enterprise Application Development with Ext JS and Spring.pdf', '4.8 MB', '446', '2013', 'English', 'PDF', 13, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1432/6555695326f2a8c.jpg', 'Spring and ExtJS are cutting edge frameworks that allow us to build high performance web applications for modern devices, that are now consuming data at a faster rate than ever before. It is the appropriate time for you to understand how to best leverage these technologies when architecting, designing, and developing large scale web development projects.', 0, 0),
(171, 'Google Maps JavaScript API Cookbook', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150627/Google Maps JavaScript API Cookbook.pdf', '9.3 MB', '316', '2013', 'English', 'PDF', 24, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1435/13558eaba905c57.jpg', 'Day by day, the use of location data is becoming more and more popular, and Google is one of the main game changers in this area. The Google Maps JavaScript API is one of the most functional and robust mapping APIs used among Geo developers. With Google Maps, you can build location-based apps, maps for mobile apps, visualize geospatial data, and customize your own maps.', 0, 0),
