(568, 'Pro Linux System Administration', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20170314/Pro Linux System Administration.pdf', '24.9 MB', '998', '2017', 'English', 'PDF', 87, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/Pro-Linux-System-Administration.jpg', 'Implement a SOHO or SMB Linux infrastructure to expand your business and associated IT capabilities. Backed by the expertise and experienced guidance of the authors, this book provides everything you need to move your business forward.', 0, 0),
(569, 'Beginning Fedora Desktop', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150519/Beginning Fedora Desktop.pdf', '24.1 MB', '504', '2014', 'English', 'PDF', 90, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1432/91555bfa84a077a.jpg', 'Beginning Fedora Desktop: Fedora 20 Edition is a complete guide to using the Fedora 20 Desktop Linux release as your daily driver for multimedia, productivity, social networking, the GNOME 3 desktop, administrative tasks, and more. Author and Linux expert Richard Petersen delves into the operating system as a whole and offers you a complete treatment of Fedora 20 Desktop configuration and use.', 0, 0),
(570, 'A Practical Guide to Fedora and Red Hat Enterprise Linux, 6th Edition', 'http://file.allitebooks.com/20150519/A Practical Guide to Fedora and Red Hat Enterprise Linux, 6th Edition.pdf', '14.1 MB', '1320', '2012', 'English', 'PDF', 90, 'http://www.allitebooks.com/wp-content/uploads/1432/91555bfa2bd333f.jpg', 'In this book, one of the world&#8217;s leading Linux experts brings together all the knowledge you need to master Fedora or Red Hat Enterprise Linux and succeed with it in the real world. Best-selling author Mark Sobell explains Linux clearly and effectively, focusing on skills you&#8217;ll actually use as a user, programmer, or administrator. Now an even more versatile learning resource, this edition adds skill objectives at the beginning of each chapter.', 0, 0);
